50|$|Some {{types of}} rice dishes require special ways of {{preparation}} {{and are not}} suited to the mode of cooking used by electric/gas <b>rice</b> <b>cookers.</b> These recipes include, e.g., risotto, paella, and stuffed peppers (capsicums). They must be cooked by hand.|$|R
